commit.message:
Adding stacking of http query values. If multiple keys are defined, they are added to an array.

?tag=thing1&tag=thing2
=> {:tag => ['thing1', 'thing2']}

Exposed the parse method (converting Processing code to JavaScript) via Processing.parse(). It can be used like so:

  Processing.parse("float foo = 2.3; int test = (int)foo;")
  // => "var foo = 2.3; var test = 0|foo;"
